  notes: >
    v1.0 release. Cases corpus mirrored on Hugging Face at
    https://huggingface.co/datasets/eyuansu71/logdx-ci. The repository
    pins three release-gate scripts (validate_committed_diagnosis_
    provider_errors.py, validate_eval_manifest_consistency.py,
    validate_diagnosis_vs_context_consistency.py) and one historical-
    exclusion manifest documenting 20 cases removed by 2026-06-09 /
    2026-06-10 cleanups.
